they put in the words "gas station"

00:14:32.260 --> 00:14:35.470
but historically the term
of reference to be able

00:14:35.470 --> 00:14:39.190
to find appropriate images
may be "filling station."

00:14:39.190 --> 00:14:43.770 position:56%
Same thing with using terms like
"hair salon" versus "a beauty shop."

00:14:43.770 --> 00:14:49.510 position:61%
And so you can get a broader range
sometimes if you situate it more closer

00:14:49.510 --> 00:14:53.100
to the historical context and
the verbiage that was used then.

00:14:53.100 --> 00:14:57.630 position:58%
And that's a challenge for teachers
to be able to negotiate through that.

00:14:57.630 --> 00:15:02.250 position:61%
But starting off with topics from a
developmentally appropriate perspective

00:15:02.250 --> 00:15:07.940 position:56%
