00:30:02.140 --> 00:30:05.240
of the wonderful classroom
applications of Library

00:30:05.240 --> 00:30:10.510
of Congress primary sources
in Cabell County schools.

00:30:10.510 --> 00:30:18.120 position:75%
Two unique aspects of the past and present
project were that there was a huge collaboration

00:30:18.120 --> 00:30:20.450 position:59%
between the primary source teachers --

00:30:20.450 --> 00:30:24.450
excuse me, the pre-service
teachers at Marshall University

00:30:24.450 --> 00:30:27.920 position:75%
and the in-service teachers across the district.

00:30:27.920 --> 00:30:30.680 position:61%
