reflect, and ask good topic related questions

00:36:02.510 --> 00:36:06.100 position:75%
and provide targeted reasons for their thinking.

00:36:06.100 --> 00:36:10.010
Allowing children to get
hands on with primary sources

00:36:10.010 --> 00:36:14.320
and providing question starters are
developmentally appropriate ways

00:36:14.320 --> 00:36:19.250 position:56%
to make deeper thinking and learning
more accessible for young learners.

