00:37:03.420 --> 00:37:09.670 position:67%
And each includes age appropriate primary
sources, historical background information,

00:37:09.670 --> 00:37:15.300 position:59%
teaching ideas for the early childhood
classroom, and analysis tools.

00:37:15.300 --> 00:37:20.830 position:58%
The children's lives set features the
ways that children worked, played,

00:37:20.830 --> 00:37:23.410 position:61%
