00:45:27.190 --> 00:45:29.420
&gt;&gt; Oh, excellent.

00:45:29.420 --> 00:45:31.980
Yes. Oh, excellent question.

00:45:31.980 --> 00:45:35.090
And thank you for that question.

00:45:35.090 --> 00:45:44.660 position:75%
Having children be able to have in front of them
actual images where they can circle, explore,

00:45:44.660 --> 00:45:48.230 position:70%
